Package: loon.ggplot
Type: Package
Title: A Grammar of Interactive Graphics
Version: 1.3.0
Date: 2020-07-17
Authors@R: c(
  person('Zehao', 'Xu', email = 'z267xu@uwaterloo.ca', role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person('R. Wayne', 'Oldford', email = 'rwoldford@uwaterloo.ca', role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: Provides a bridge between the 'loon' and  'ggplot2' packages.  Extends the grammar of ggplot to add clauses to create interactive `loon` plots. Existing ggplots can be turned into interactive 'loon' plots and 'loon' plots into static ggplots; the function 'loon.ggplot()' is the bridge from one plot structure to the other.
License: GPL-2
BugReports: https://github.com/great-northern-diver/loon.ggplot/issues
